Ranger Help for: whirl
======================

SYNTAX:      whirl <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     30
SKILL TYPE:  attack

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to execute a spinning melee attack against
a target, dealing a combination of slash and blunt damage. The whirling
motion uses both the blade and the momentum of the swing to inflict
dual damage types. Whirl is effective against opponents with resistance
to a single damage type. The Ranger must be in combat and wielding a
melee weapon to use this skill.
